Meet @karolinevitto, the #BFCNEWGEN designer who has presented a new capsule collection alongside Pull&Bear under the ‘Canvas for Creativity’ initiative.

Her work explores femininity through a body-aware design approach. Garments are conceived to adapt, sculpt and move with the body rather than reshape it.

